            AMIGAPUNT MENUS

There are three menus:


    PROJECT, EDIT, & SPECIAL.




PROJECT MENU:

    NEW RACE:   You'll be given an option to save the currently
            defined race. The current race is then cleared
            and you are presented with a 'clean' slate to
            enter details for a new race.

            The preferences are set to the default.

            SHORTHAND COMMAND: RIGHT AMIGA & N.


    OPEN RACE:  Load a previously save race from disk. Selection
            is from a file requester.

            SHORTHAND COMMAND: RIGHT AMIGA & O.

    SAVE RACE:  Saves the current race under the current file
            name. If no file name has been given then
            the file is saved in the current directory
            as 'AMIGAPUNTRACEFILE'.

            SHORTHAND COMMAND: RIGHT AMIGA & S.


    SAVE RACE AS:   Same as above, but you are requested to
            enter the path and/ or file name for the race.

    PRINT RACE: Dumps the current race to the PRINTER.

            SHORTHAND COMMAND: RIGHT AMIGA & P

    INFORMATION:    Tries to display this file via a primitive
            text reader. If it fails to find the file
            you are given the option to select another
            text path/ file name!

            SHORTHAND COMMAND: RIGHT AMIGA & I

    PREFERENCES:
            Two sub-items are available:

            EDIT PREFERENCES:

                Displays the current 'Factors' which
                may be re-defined by the user.

            SAVE PREFERENCES:

                Saves the current 'Factors' which will
                become the defaults.


    HAPPY PUNTING:  Quit AmigaPunt!





EDIT MENU:

    DELETE CURRENT HORSE:

            Deletes (scratches) the current horse after
            user confirmation. Use a little care as
            there is no 'undo' function for this option.

            SHORTHAND COMMAND: RIGHT AMIGA & X

    DISPLAY/ EDIT RACE CARD:

            Displays the currently defined race for
            editing.

            SHORTHAND COMMAND: RIGHT AMIGA & D

    EDIT:
            Places the cursor on the first item
            on the current screen/ window ready
            for editing. Each carriage return
            moves the cursor to the next data field.

SPECIAL:

    RATE CURRENT RACE:

            Rates the current race, and returns to
            the Race Screen/ Window, displaying the
            results.

            SHORTHAND COMMAND: RIGHT AMIGA & =

    SORT HORSE BY:

            TAB NUMBER:

             Sorts, stores & display the current
            list of horses by the TAB number.


            NAME:

             Sorts, stores & display the current
            list of horses by their names.

            RATING

             Sorts, stores & display the current
            list of horses by the ratings.

